  - “Portfolio site from scratch” → Create Next.js App Router project, Tailwind theme with personal branding, deploy to Vercel.
  - “Clone e-commerce structure” → Reproduce architecture from source repo, add base components (NavBar, ProductCard), and integrate Tailwind theme.
